title.narrative: Programme Management and Monitoring of the Hunger Safety Net Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Programme Management and Monitoring of the Hunger Safety Net Programme) is a component of Hunger Safety Net Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £8,404,696. This component benefits Kenya, and works in the following sector(s): Social Protection. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, DAI Europe, European Commission - Directorate-General for International Cooperation and Development. The start date is 23-08-2013 and the end date is 31-03-2019.
